editorialNotes.short: Your child’s unique world—in words, sounds and images.

editorialNotes.tagline: Create and rule your own universe
editorialNotes.standard: We love learning about the celestial bodies in our own galaxy, but we’ve always dreamed of building our own. SPACE gives us the power to create stunningly detailed stars and planets, forging a virtual universe that follows the laws of astrophysics. It’s a heady thrill to be the master of our own miniature heavens—whipping up red dwarfs, gas giants, and comets that blaze through the cosmos at the tap of a finger.

name: Touch, Look, Listen ~ My First Words

ios.subtitle: Build up a farm & grow veggies

editorialNotes.standard: Even a kid can run Dr. Panda’s farm, and ours love being in charge. Who wouldn’t? Milking cows, gathering honey, making jam—it’s easy to figure out and fun selling food to unlock new activities. Plus, the papercraft-style animals couldn’t be more adorable.
editorialNotes.short: Grow wheat, collect milk, and make bread on your own farm.
